<sect2>
 <title>Brief overview of probes</title> 

<para>Two major uses for probes:
      
      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem><para>
          To interface with an object </para></listitem>
        <listitem><para>
          To create a GUI to an object</para></listitem>
      </itemizedlist>

      Interface with an object of two types:

      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem><para>VarProbe: Probes an instance
        variable</para></listitem>

        <listitem><para>MessageProbe: Probes a method</para></listitem>
      </itemizedlist>

      GUI utilities:
      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem><para>ProbeMap: Collection of Var and
        MessageProbes</para></listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
    </para>

</sect2>

